      "parameters": {
        "description": "Returns documents related to the Holland RIASEC personality model and the Saudi Digital Skills Framework. The data includes explanations of the six Holland personality types (Realistic, Investigative, Artistic, Social, Enterprising, and Conventional), descriptions of personality traits and interests, and information about digital job families, roles, and required skills in the Saudi digital sector. These documents help interpret users’ Holland personality results and connect them with suitable digital career paths and skills based on the Saudi Digital Skills Framework."
